reviewText: We are Gaither fans - the type of fans who will drive to a state next door or several hours away and stay for a Gaither Fest of 2 days of Praise and Worship of our Lord. But this DVD is the absolute favorite among friends and strangers we've showed it to. We keep buying more as we keep Passin' the Faith Along. Hubby prefers the CD for his car and we both love the DVD for our home.
Title: N/A

reviewText: Bill Gaither has brought so much to all his gospel fans and all that he helps. I have never seen a bad video that this man has made. He has enriched our lives so much with his Gaither Family.I have never heard so many great singers in one room.I have heard songs that are new and from the past. I don't believe there has ever been a poor written gospel song. The talent is just beyond amazing and I love everything they sing. I started collecting the Gaithers and I now own about 30 of them.The best part about music is you never get tired of listening to it.I will keep on collecting him as long as he keeps on making them.

reviewText: If you like Homecoming music, this DVD is for you... They sing a lot (like Heaven DVD). But if you want to watch the Gaither Vocal Band... they sing just one and do back vocal to another (with Russ Taff). The title song is very good, besides three or for others, including a beatiful song by The Isaacs. In other hand, there's a terrible trio and some others songs to hear just once. I recommend only if you want to complete your Gaither Collection.
Title: N/A

reviewText: This one really doesn`t stand out as other of his show do. Many unknown to me groups and names who I see for the first time. Same tempo and sound even the Isaacs sound weak, I`ve watched half of the show on youtube and will definitely not get this one. For some it might please them but not with me.When not sure upon a show just go to youtube and enter the title of the dvd you`ll get the whole show so your choice will be easier to make.If by chance you don`t buy this one the Gaither family will still eat three meals a day. I thought Andre rieu had many Dvd`s out the Gaithers have close to 200 shows on dvd or VHS.
summary: Did not get hooked on this one
